<function>

access:   public

name: date

param: string, $spec

param: string, $format, NULL

return: string

</function>

Outputs a formatted date using [[php date()]] conventions.

* Parameters:

 * string //$spec//: Any date-time string suitable for strtotime().

 * string //$format//: An optional custom [[php date()]] formatting string; null by default.

* Returns string: The formatted date string.

Outputs a formatted date using [[php date()]] conventions.